AViS CHANGELOG


VERSION 0.02
General
- Changed name from MDVis to AViS
- Improved memory management
- New progress bar replacing animation bar when busy
File I/O
- Added simulation box information
- Better GROMACS importer
- Better remote file handling
Visualization
- Allow animated simulation box
- Render and Information tab now contain actual stuff
- Render GLSL to gif/avi
- Improve selection control
Analysis
- Scripts (re)load in background
- New nodes: SetRadiusScale, ToAdjacencyList, ToLinkedList
- Particle input filter now works
- Improved data caching for Run All
- Execution now blocks animation controls

